## Lydia's Home Security Device

#### Lydia has designed a home security device. The device displays a green light if the house is properly secured (all windows closed and doors locked) and a red light if the home is not secured.

#### After an initial round of testing, color blind users reported not being able to tell whether the home was secured or not because the red and green lights looked too similar.

#### Now Lydia needs to make a decision about what to do with this new information

